## Skills System

Skills are Claude instruction packages in `skills/`. Registry: `skills/registry.json`.

Available skills:
- **prototype-generator** — Generate branded Figma prototypes from briefs
- **coded-prototype-generator** — Generate interactive Vue prototypes on CF Pages
- **design-critique** — Review designs for compliance and quality
- **prd-writer** — Write/review/refactor PRDs
- **kb** — Search the GitBook knowledgebase for platform answers
- **tutor** — Adaptive FT CRM tutoring with quizzes and scenarios
- **skill-architect** — Create new skills (the skill factory)

## Commands

```bash
npm run build:tokens        # Rebuild CSS/SCSS/TS from token JSON
npm run snap -- <path>       # Screenshot a platform page
npm run snap:login           # Open browser for CRM authentication
npm run snap:proto           # Screenshot prototype pages
npm run snap:compare         # Compare before/after screenshots
npm run snap:paste <img>     # Paste screenshot into Figma
npm run scan:source          # Analyze Vue source files → page-manifest.json
npm run gen:tracker          # Auto-generate composition-tracker.md
npm run audit:parity         # Compare Figma vs Vue component specs
npm run mcp:health           # MCP connectivity check + cleanup
npm run mcp:status           # MCP status only
node scripts/scan.js         # Discover platform pages → scan-manifest.json
node scripts/clone-batch.js  # Batch-clone Vue pages for coded prototypes
```
